### [Ezra Chapter 5](../../../bib/kjv/ezr005.htm#001.md)

[Ezra](../../../bib/kjv/ezr001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">ezr 5:0</span></span>

Overview

[Ezr 5:1](../../../bib/kjv/ezr005.htm#001.md), Zerubbabel and Jeshua,
incited by Haggai and Zechariah, set forward the building of the temple;
[Ezr 5:3](../../../bib/kjv/ezr005.htm#003.md), Tatnai and Shethar-boznai
are not able to hinder the Jews; [Ezr
5:6](../../../bib/kjv/ezr005.htm#006.md), Their letter to Darius against
the Jews.

